column5: Hey All,  I went out to one of my favourite ponds after waking up this afternoon. Anyway, was able to catch 4 really nice sized smallies  and 2 smaller ones. All in all it was great to finally catch something and be out......
What no pics? Come on, you know we love pics. Well then you'll just have to tell us where your ponds are
Standard KW rule NO PHOTO =NO FISH . We need visual evidence. Eyewitness testimony is so unreliable.
There should be a minimum of 6 pics in this report!!!  ... and how much pepperspray was used to subdue the perps???
forgot the camera....next time i should bring someone to take the pictures.....lol  GCD.....again with the pepper spray.....BTW I HATE THAT STUFF.... I HAVE NEVER USED IT AFTER BEING SPRAYED
I take it you prefer the baton!!!
Well, if you ever see how well he twirls it......and then tosses it into the air and catches it.....
hahaha...no, i've used it once and that was to break a window...lol..... but i twirl it real purdy....he he
I just like to rib you aboot the pepperspray because yer the Fuzz  I've never sprayed or been sprayed with it, but I'm sure it's some nasty stuff!
